---
layout: recipe
title: Lemon Blueberry Muffins
image: lemon-blueberry-muffins.png
tags: Dessert
category: Dessert
yield: 15 Muffins
preptime: 30 Minutes
cooktime: 25 Minutes

directions:
- Prepare the Crumble Topping and set aside.
- Prepare the muffins.
- Prepare the glaze.
- After the muffins have cooled for 5 minutes, drizzle the glaze over the muffins.

components:
- Muffin Crumble Topping
- Lemon Blueberry Muffins
- Lemon Glaze

---
